    body
        div.container
            include ./navbar.pug

            div.my-5
                div.row.p-4.pb-0.pe-lg-0.pt-lg-5.align-items-center.rounded-3.border.shadow-lg
                    div.col-lg-7.p-3.p-lg-5.pt-lg-3
                        h1.display-4.fw-bold.lh-1 Border hero with cropped image and shadows
                        p.lead
                            | Quickly design and customize responsive mobile-first sites with Bootstrap, the world&rsquo;s most popular front-end open source toolkit, featuring Sass variables and mixins, responsive grid system, extensive prebuilt components, and powerful JavaScript plugins.
                        div.d-grid.gap-2.d-md-flex.justify-content-md-start.mb-4.mb-lg-3
                            button.btn.btn-outline-primary.btn-lg.px-4.me-md-2.fw-bold(type='button') 
                                a.nav-link(href='/services' aria-current='page') Our Services
                            button.btn.btn-outline-secondary.btn-lg.px-4(type='button') 
                                a.nav-link(href='/contact' aria-current='page') Contact Us
                    div.col-lg-4.offset-lg-1.p-0.overflow-hidden.shadow-lg
                        img.rounded-lg-3(src='../assets/bootstrap-docs.png' alt='img' width='720')



            include ./footer.pug